post.body:
Sorry if the "New users count record" posts are boring. I'll post it for each 20 new users.

Also I'm not only going to use Peeper for only post these messages or to change little things. A lot of features are going to be introduced by @Plasmmer: when the --debug mode works properly. Also a app for creating Coffeescript apps with a event sheet editor is being planned, and it will help less-hard contributions/development to Peeper and other services.

The changes that are comming:
* Post peers counter;
* Posts now called "peeps";
* "Verified public profile" badge;
* Open Badges field in profile;
* Site, birthday, Bitcoin address and other new profile fields;

Please stay tunned by following this profile.

